<sect2 id="gimp-layer-next">
  <title>Select Next Layers</title>

  <indexterm>
    <primary>Layer</primary>
    <secondary>Stack managing</secondary>
    <tertiary>Next layers</tertiary>
  </indexterm>

  <para>
    The <guimenuitem>Select Next Layers</guimenuitem> command selects the
    layers below the selected layers in the layer stack. The command
    highlights the layers in the Layers Dialog and makes it the new active
    selection. If the selected layers end at the bottom of the stack, this
    menu entry is disabled.
  </para>

  <sect3>
    <title>Activating the Command</title>
    <para>
      You can access this command
    </para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          From the main menu through
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Layer</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>Stack</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>Select Next Layers</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          By using the keyboard shortcut <keycap>PgDn</keycap>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
